==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Foully
<hw>Foul"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v.</pos> <def>In a foul manner;
filthily; nastily; shamefully; unfairly; dishonorably.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I <qex>foully</qex> wronged him; do forgive me, do.</q>
<rj><qau>Gay.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Foul-mouthed</ent>⟦br⟧
